content:
Launch LWC OmniScripts from Lightning and Experience Pages

You can launch LWC OmniScripts on Community and Lightning pages using the generated OmniScript Component or the LWC OmniScript Wrapper component.

Use this table to determine which component meets your requirements:

Generated OmniScript LWC:
Automatically passes RecordId into the OmniScript's Data JSON
Displays one layout (Lightning or Newport)
Not directly URL addressable
Cannot accept parameters

Vlocity LWC OmniScript Wrapper:
Accepts additional URL parameters
Loads different OmniScripts based on parameters
Accepts prefill information
Compatible with LWC Save For Later prefill functionality

Add an LWC OmniScript to a Lightning or Experience Page by adding the generated component.
Launch an LWC OmniScript with LWC OmniScript Wrapper using the Vlocity LWC OmniScript Wrapper component.
Display Inline OmniScripts on Lightning and Community Pages, enabling them to run inline without leaving the page context. The record id passes into the inline OmniScript as a Context Id automatically.
Embed an OmniScript in a Lightning Web Component using the generated OmniScript Lightning Web Component.
title: Launching LWC OmniScripts
